trans-unit.source: Represents security information for client application services, which includes role information.
trans-unit.target: Representerar säkerhetsinformation för klienten programtjänster, som innehåller rollinformation om.

trans-unit.source: When you validate a user in client application services, the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> or the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> sets the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: När du validerar användare i klienten programtjänster, den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>eller <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>anger den `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap till en instans av den här klassen</xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> initializes the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A> property to a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientFormsIdentity> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>Initierar <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A>egenskapen till en ny instans av <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientFormsIdentity>klassen.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientFormsIdentity> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> initializes the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A> property to the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> object returned by the `static` <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetCurrent?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>initierar den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A>egenskapen till den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>objektet som returneras av den `static` <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetCurrent?displayProperty=fullName>metod.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetCurrent?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.Identity%2A> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>

trans-unit.source: You will not typically access this class directly.
trans-unit.target: Du kommer inte normalt att komma åt den här klassen direkt.

trans-unit.source: Normally, you will call the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A> method of the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> returned by the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Normalt sett du anropar den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>metod för den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>returneras av den `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, you can cast the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property value to a ClientRolePrincipal reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.IsInRole%2A> method explicitly, as demonstrated in the Example section.
trans-unit.target: Men du kan omvandla den <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>egenskapsvärdet till en ClientRolePrincipal-referens för att anropa den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.IsInRole%2A>metoden uttryckligen som visas i avsnittet exempel.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal.IsInRole%2A> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>

trans-unit.source: Represents the current user.
trans-unit.target: Representerar den aktuella användaren.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the user represented by the <xref href="System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal"></xref> is in the specified role.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om användaren som representeras av den <xref href="System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal"> </xref> i den angivna rollen.

trans-unit.source: Normally, you will call the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A> method of the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> returned by the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Normalt sett du anropar den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>metod för den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>returneras av den `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, you can cast the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property value to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> reference to call this method explicitly, as demonstrated in the Example section.
trans-unit.target: Men du kan omvandla den <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>egenskapsvärdet till en <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>referens för att anropa den här metoden uttryckligen som visas i avsnittet exempel.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>

trans-unit.source: The IsInRole method will always return `false` if the user login has expired.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IsInRole returnerar alltid `false` om du loggar in som användare har upphört att gälla.

trans-unit.source: This will not occur if your application calls the <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A> method one time shortly after authentication.
trans-unit.target: Detta utförs inte om programmet anropar den <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>metoden en gång strax efter autentisering.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal.IsInRole%2A>

trans-unit.source: If your application must retrieve user roles at other times, you might want to add code to revalidate users whose login has expired.
trans-unit.target: Om ditt program måste hämta användarroller vid andra tillfällen, kanske du vill lägga till kod för att verifiera användare vars inloggningen har upphört att gälla.

trans-unit.source: If all valid users are assigned to roles, you can determine whether the login has expired by calling the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Om alla giltiga användare har tilldelats roller, kan du bestämma om inloggningen har upphört att gälla genom att anropa den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If no roles are returned, the login has expired.
trans-unit.target: Om inga roller returneras inloggningen har gått ut.

trans-unit.source: For an example of this functionality, see the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Ett exempel på den här funktionen finns i <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A>metod.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider.GetRolesForUser%2A>

trans-unit.source: This functionality is only necessary if you have selected **Require users to log on again whenever the server cookie expires** in your application configuration.
trans-unit.target: Den här funktionen är bara nödvändigt om du har valt **användare måste logga in igen när servern cookien förfaller** i tillämpningsprogrammets konfiguration.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Configure Client Application Services](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [så här: konfigurera klienten programtjänster](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The role to check.
trans-unit.target: Rolltjänsten för att kontrollera.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the user is in the specified role; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the user is not in the specified role or is not authenticated.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om användaren är i den angivna rollen; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om användaren finns inte i den angivna rollen eller inte har autentiserats.
